Package org.kawanfw.commons.api.client

Provides class and interfaces to configure the Awake Commons parameters on the client side.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    HttpProtocolParameters
    Allows to define some parameters for the session: Buffer size when uploading files.
    HttpProxy
    Allows to define a proxy with or without authentication.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    InvalidLoginException
    Signals that the Server Manager refused the (username, password) login or that the user is not any more logged.
    RemoteException
    Signals that an Exception has been thrown by a remote method on the server.
